dialogue: A dark road, on a rainy night? It could have been a hit and run.
He was playing out a hit and run.
Kendall was 5'5. If she was hunched over and the car was an SUV or a truck, she could've easily been hit smack across the head and torso. Look at the way her shoulders are fractured...
I'm sorry, are you a doctor?
Well, then I think we should leave this to the professionals who actually examined the body.
Good, because we're not here to solve a mystery. All we're here to do is decide if we're positive that James Sythe killed Kendall Carter.
I'm not. Old Quarry Road feeds into the highway. When traffic's heavy, GPS will send you that way. It can get busy.
